msgid "Sync theme files"
msgstr "同步主题文件"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Sync individual files from SDK to dev server.\n"
"\n"
"    Send an array of files with path, content (base64 for binary), and "
"checksum.\n"
"    Files are written to the dev theme directory and trigger appropriate "
"reload.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    从 SDK 向开发服务器同步单个文件。发送包含路径、内容（二进制文件使用 "
"base64 编码）和校验和的文件数组。文件将写入开发主题目录并触发适当的重新加"
"载。\n"
"    "

msgid "Files synced successfully"
msgstr "文件同步成功"

msgid "Invalid request"
msgstr "请求无效"

msgid "Sync full theme archive"
msgstr "同步完整主题存档"

msgid ""
"\n"
"    Sync a complete theme as a ZIP archive.\n"
"\n"
"    The archive replaces the entire dev theme directory.\n"
"    Send the ZIP file as raw binary in the request body.\n"
"    "
msgstr ""
"\n"
"    将完整的主题作为 ZIP 存档进行同步。该存档将替换整个开发主题目录。请将 "
"ZIP 文件以原始二进制格式发送到请求体中。\n"
"\n"
"    将完整的主题作为 ZIP 存档进行同步。该存档将替换整个开发主题目录。请将 "
"ZIP 文件以原始二进制格式发送到请求体中。\n"
